# DELTA Protocol line-ending and byte-stability policy.
#
# Rule:
# - Source/docs may be normalized to LF.
# - Public proof artifacts MUST preserve exact bytes.
#
# Public verifiers hash bytes, not visual text. Therefore proof artifacts
# must not be changed by Git CRLF/LF conversion.

# Normal text files
README.md text eol=lf
src/** text eol=lf
docs/**/*.html text eol=lf
docs/**/*.css text eol=lf
docs/**/*.js text eol=lf
docs/**/*.md text eol=lf

# Public proof artifacts: preserve exact bytes.
# Do NOT normalize line endings here.
spec/** -text
examples/** -text

# Binary artifacts
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.zip binary